  "prompt": "What is a teacher?",
  "response": "A teacher is a professional who helps students acquire knowledge, develop skills, and cultivate attitudes and values. Teachers play a vital role in the educational system and can work at various levels, from early childhood education to higher education. Their responsibilities typically include planning lessons, delivering instruction, assessing student performance, providing feedback, and fostering a supportive and engaging learning environment. Teachers may also serve as mentors and advisors, guiding students in their personal development and helping them navigate academic challenges.",
